ues could force shutdowns amid spiking global LNG prices.","summary":"Fertiliser stocks Chambal, RCF, GNFC may dip as LNG supply disruption from Qatar impacts urea production.\nIndia's fertiliser firms cut output; prolonged supply issues could force shutdowns amid spiking global LNG prices.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/fertiliser-stocks-chambal-rcf-gnfc-lng-supply-disruption-threatens-urea-output-qatar-ws-l-19862441.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-05T09:02:09","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"514806","title":"RCF announces Shri Ajit A. Thatte's promotion to GM, effective March 1, 2026.\nAjit Thatte has 34+ years of experience and holds degrees in Petrochemical Engg. & Industrial Safety.","summary":"RCF announces Shri Ajit A. Thatte's promotion to GM, effective March 1, 2026.\nAjit Thatte has 34+ years of experience and holds degrees in Petrochemical Engg. & Industrial Safety.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=4a771815-4491-419a-a2c8-5437daded1fc.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-02T15:40:36","source":"BSE"},{"id":"260216154625690","title":"The Uttar Pradesh government has banned sales of non-subsidized fertilizers by urea manufacturers, impacting investor sentiment and nutrient efficiency.\nKey fertilizer firms like National Fertilizers, Coromandel International, and Chambal Fertilisers face challenges, with UP's market for non-subsidized fertilizers being relatively small.","summary":"The Uttar Pradesh government has banned sales of non-subsidized fertilizers by urea manufacturers, impacting investor sentiment and nutrient efficiency.\nKey fertilizer firms like National Fertilizers, Coromandel International, and Chambal Fertilisers face challenges, with UP's market for non-subsidized fertilizers being relatively small.","url":"https://indianexpress.com/article/explained/explained-economics/how-the-fertilisers-industry-has-become-synonymous-with-controls-10534028/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-15T05:54:38","